The,TomTom,Sports,Watch,records,tracks,and,synchronizes,data,of,the,sports,and,fitness,activities,of,users,This,data,is,then,stored,and,analyzed,in,the,cloud,using,the,TomTom,MySports,Cloud,API,The,API,allows,users,to,organize,data,and,access,analytical,data,and,visual,summaries,of,the,progress,goals,and,achievements,of,their,sports,and,fitness,programs,Its,access,requires,TomTom,account,sign,in,and,OAuth,authorization,The,API,sends,requests,in,HTTP,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,or,CSV,format